general area of the southern arizona desert since 1980 according to 
figures released last summer by the us border patrol 
on sunday authorities loaded the latest group onto a bus and 
drove them to the border city of nogales 
thirtyone walked silently through a revolving steel gate into 
the mexican state of sonora the other five followed after 
videotaping interviews 
we have to think it over said gilberto perez 28 of the 
possibility he would try again to reach the agricultural belt 
surrounding phoenix 
authorities said all 36 including one woman came from the state 
