they have flown in from around america each 
filling two airline seats to lose weight and call attention to dick 
gregorys call for a national war on obesity 
they are a dozen very fat people from 268 to 600 pounds to whom 
gregory has offered a free last chance to lose weight a service 
the comedianturnednutritionist says the government should be 
rendering 
i never knew this kind of obesity exists gregory said monday 
as he welcomed some arrivals at laguardia airport im saying the 
government has to come in and get involved 
since the case of walter hudson one of several highly publicized 
