and exercise routine devised by gregory 
gregory said the treatment program would cost him hundreds of 
thousands of dollars he said part of the tab would be covered by 
his successful nutritional food business 
gregory said he chose these obese people because they had the 
saddest stories and because they seemed healthy enough to diet 
safely 
some talked about suicide he said one lady said she 
prayed she could get cancer i thought it was so she could die she 
said it was so she could get thin 
gregory said the federal government should establish an 
institute on obesity and a clearing house for information on the 
problem he also called for a congressional investigation of what he 
