would say thats a considerably low estimate 
what we are hoping to do in horse cave is to establish a 
national museum and education center we are hoping to help raise a 
few generations of people who understand that the importance of 
understanding the land is more than just the surface when you look 
at the surface all you see is a reflection of the rocks that 
underly it 
