to see a mountain lion track ive only seen a mountain lion once 
and i feel privileged to have seen that 
great basin also offers alpine lakes most above the 10000foot 
mark stella and teresa lakes are within a mile or so of roads but 
some are a hard days hike distant in the back country five miles 
or more and considerable elevation hendricks said 
